ields, such as quantum computing or drug development.\n   c) Propose a novel research direction that could emerge from the development of quantum biological diagnostics.\n\nEnsure your response demonstrates a deep understanding of both quantum mechanics and biology, as well as their potential interactions in living systems. Use appropriate scientific terminology and provide clear explanations for complex concepts. Be innovative in your approach while maintaining scientific plausibility.\n\nFormat your response with clear headings for each section. Your total response should be between 950-1200 words."

    @staticmethod
